quran[24]{c,v,t}:
  37,103,"Nde Й“e jebbilaninoo yamiroore Alla nden, Ibraahiima hippiri geЙ—al makko, tiinde nden, fii hirsugol mo."
  37,104,"Men noddi Ibraahiima fewndo o hittiniraynoo waЙ—ugol yamiroore Alla nden, ka hirsugol geЙ—aljo makko on, wiide: ko an yo Ibraahiima!"
  37,105,"Pellet, a laatinirii koyЙ—ol maa ngol, fiЙ“ugol hirsude geЙ—aljo maa on. Awa ko wano Men yoЙ“itirt maa non firtingol ma nden huunde saЙ—tunde, woni ko Men yoЙ“itirta moЖґЖґinooЙ“e Й“en; Men Й“oora Й“e e kulaleeji e saЙ—teendeeji."
  37,106,"Pellet, ko Й—um Й—oo woni jarrabuyee Й“annguЙ—o on. Ibraahiima hawrii e mun."
  37,107,"Men soktiri Ismaa'iila, dammol mawnungol, ko hirsee, hara wanaa kanko."
  37,108,"Men accani Ibraahiima, mantoore labaande, e mofte sakkitiiЙ—e Й—en."
  37,109,"Alla hiwrike mo, O du'anike mo kadi kisal e kala lorra."
  37,110,"Ko wano Men yoЙ“itiri Ibraahiima e Й—oftaare makko nden, Men yoЙ“itirta moЖґЖґinooЙ“e Й“en."
  37,111,"Kanko Ibraahiima, ko o jeyanooЙ—o e jeyaaЙ“e Amen gomЙ—imЙ“e, hunnuЙ“e sifaaji jeyeede Alla."
  37,112,"Men wewlintiniri mo geЙ—aljo goo, wonoowo Annabaajo, e jeyaaЙ—o moЖґЖґo; on woni Ishaaqa. ЖЉum ko njoЙ“di Й—oftagol mo Alla ngol, ka hirsugol Ismaa'iila, Й“iЙ—Й—o makko bajjo on nun."
  37,113,"Men jippini barki e makko, e dow geЙ—al makko Ishaaqa. Men Й—uЙ—Й—inani Й“e neema; wano Й—uuЙ—ireede Й“iЙ—Й“e. Hino e geyngol maЙ“Й“e ngol non, moЖґЖґinЙ—o Й—oftagpl Joomi mun, e tooГ±irЙ—o hoore-mun yeddugol faggitoo Й“anngina bone."
  37,114,"GomЙ—ii Men moЖґЖґorike e dow Muusaa, e nene gooto makko on Haaruuna, Annabaaku ngun."
  37,115,"Men daЙ—ndi Й“e, kamЙ“e e yimЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en, maccinireede Fir'awna, e yoolagol."
  37,116,"Men walli Й“e e Fir'awna e konu mun, Й“e fooli ayЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en."
  37,117,"Men okki Muusaa e neene gooto makko on Haaruuna, Deftere Tawreeta nden, immorde ka Alla, Й“anngunde, nde jilЙ“uya alah e mayre."
  37,118,"Men fewniri Й“e, e laawol focciingol ngol. Ngol woni laawol diina lislaamu kan, Й—owirayngol e welayee seniiЙ—o taguЙ—o On."
  37,119,"Men accani Й“e mantoore e jantoore labaande, e mofte sakkitiiЙ“e Й“en."
  37,120,"Alla hiwrorike Й“e hiwraandu teddundu, O mantii Й“e, O du'oranike Й“e hisugol e kala bone."
  37,121,"Ko wano Men yoЙ“itiri non Muusaa e Haaruuna, woni ko Men yoЙ“itirta moЖґЖґinooЙ“e Й—fotagol Joomi mun Й“en."
  37,122,"Muusaa e Haaruuna, ko jeyanooЙ“e e jeyaaЙ“e Amen gomЙ—imЙ“e Alla, golliri sari'a Makko on."
  37,123,"Pellet, Ilyaasa kadi, ko jeyanooЙ—o e NulaaЙ“e Alla Й“en. Alla moЖґЖґorino e makko Annabaaku e Nulal."
  37,124,"Janto nde o maakannoo yimЙ“e mako Й“en o nulaa e mun Й“en, ka Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila: Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, e on hulirtaa Alla Й—oftagol yamirooje Makko Й—en, wano wootinЙ—ingol Mo, e woЙ—Й—itagol haЙ—aaЙ—i Makko Й—in, wano sirku?"
  37,125,"E on reway sanamuuru mon wi'eteende "Ba'ala" ndun, accon Й—on Alla, Й“urЙ—o moЖґЖґude tagu On?"
  37,126,"Ko Alla woni Joomi mon, woni taguЙ—o on, O tagi baabiraaЙ“e mon Й“en ado Й—um. Ko On hanndi e reweede, wanaa goЙ—Й—um goo, wano sanamuuji mon, Й—i duncataa Й—i lorrataa."